Please use the mcp server called hf-mcp-server to get the details of huggingface hosted models.
You can find the model details like full name, author, model size and params, the organization, the training data, etc.
You can also find the best model for a given task. The evaluation results are available for some models.
You can also find the recent research papers, trending papers and papers related to a given model, their details, authors, etc.